title: Mechanics of Materials 6th Edition Solutions (James Gere, Barry
description:
This is the instructors solutions manual for the 6th edition of the "Mechanics of Materials" textbook written by James M. Gere and Barry J. Goodno, published by Cengage Learning. All of the files in this torrent are in pdf form.

About a third of these solutions are exactly the same as the 7th edition of this textbook, which is the current edition. Most of the solutions in the 6th edition can be directly applied to the newest edition. If you are a Mechanical or Civil Engineer, this solutions manual is for you!
